<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Padding and Margin</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            margin: 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .box {
            width: 300px;
            background-color: lightblue;
            border: 2px solid royalblue;
        }

        .padding-all {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .padding-different {
            padding: 10px 20px 30px 40px;
        }

        .margin-all {
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .margin-different {
            margin: 10px 20px 30px 40px;
        }

        .padding-margin {
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px;
        }

        .center {
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .circle {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            border: 3px solid tomato;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: peachpuff;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 110px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>Padding and Margin</h1>

    <h2>1. Padding</h2>

    <div class="box padding-all">
        Padding: 20px
    </div>

    <h2>2. Different Padding Values</h2>

    <div class="box padding-different">
        Padding: 10px 20px 30px 40px
    </div>

    <h2>3. Margin</h2>

    <div class="box margin-all">
        Margin: 20px
    </div>

    <h2>4. Different Margin Values</h2>

    <div class="box margin-different">
        Margin: 10px 20px 30px 40px
    </div>

    <h2>5. Padding + Margin</h2>

    <div class="box padding-margin">
        Using both padding and margin together.
    </div>

    <h2>6. Center a Box</h2>

    <div class="box center">
        margin: auto
    </div>

    <h2>7. Circle Example</h2>

    <div class="circle">
        Circle
    </div>

</body>
</html>